    <header>
      <h1 class=3D"title type-heading type-heading--1">
        Convert Fahrenheit and Celsius: The easy way
      </h1>
      <div class=3D"meta">
  <div class=3D"meta-outer-wrapper">
    <div class=3D"meta-inner-wrapper">
      <div class=3D"meta-author">
          <a href=3D"https://thoughtbot.com/blog/authors/stephanie-kuroda">=
